OL,5, Historians in Hawick are working       
OL,6, through thousands of books, videos and 
OL,7, clippings in a bid to recreate Bill    
OL,8, McLaren's "chaotic" research room.     
OL,10,FThe study of the "voice of rugby" was  
OL,11,Fwhere match-day preparations took place
OL,12,Fduring his 50-year career.             
OL,14,FA recreation of the office will act as 
OL,15,Fa centrepiece of an exhibition to      
OL,16,Fcelebrate Bill's centenary.            
OL,18,FHistorian Murray Watson said he had    
OL,19,Fspent two years going through 30,000   
OL,20,Fdifferent items from the room.         
